    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>(You must have <strong>Latent Steel Release II</strong>)</em> </p><p>Beginning at 11th level, when you cast a jutsu with the Earth Release keyword that creates a construct, you can spend an additional amount of chakra equal to the rank of the jutsu cast <em>(D/C-Rank: 3, B/A-Rank: 5, S-Rank: 7)</em>. When you do, the construct gains a +1 bonus to AC and loses any vulnerability it may have to lightning.</p>",
